The command to set parameters for ``/roulette`` command.```
/roulette-setting
```will display buttons for setting parameters.

The blue buttons are the selected parameters and the gray buttons are the **not selected** buttons. By pressing the buttons, you can change the selection/unselection.
Press `[Reset]` to initialize the parameters.
Press `[Run]` to run the roulette. Roulette can also be executed by `/roulette` command.
